955-cc40eb869259","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Format Capabilities"},"id":"0b578056-0346-46e6-aaa7-c56d3d6bb5c6","type":"heading"},{"data":{"path":"/TM9tc3g65F6LdNhrixD6C5.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"In addition to simple eBooks, Atavist makes a variety of other formats available to you. The service is set up to be an outlet for all forms of written creativity, including audio and video creations, and it offers several eBook formats. You can make guides, including travel remembrances or professional-style articles about your travels with your photography displayed throughout the digital eBook. You can also use Atavist for work-related endeavors such as magazine design. There are formats on the service’s site for magazine articles and educational materials such as study guides, complete with tests. If you are more interested in family-oriented projects, such as picture books and photo albums, Atavist has the ability to make those as well.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/63986-creatavist25.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TM9tc3g65F6LdNhrixD6C5.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"TM9tc3g65F6LdNhrixD6C5","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TM9tc3g65F6LdNhrixD6C5.jpg","alt":""},"id":"f702fea4-ddb9-4986-91cb-5d7a3e314a7e","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["One great advantage of the service is that it is connected to heavily used eBook sources such as Amazon and Barnes &amp; Noble, which cater to the Kindle and Nook devices, respectively. If you want your eBook published with these services, including family-geared eBooks, you can choose to have your work there during the final publishing process. There is not a limit on what kind of format can be published to most eBook publishers, and Atavist has a system that lets you know which formats are compatible with which publishers, as well as which publishers are willing to distribute them."]},"id":"26bc7c90-1a9c-45d8-adb0-9645